{"tid":1723240,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［正視聽長文］五毛風向撚來來去去都係同一招","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T01:55:29.000Z","uid":37247,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"2c62790e546903e4ab02c8f3e270e1cf14d7133d","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"由6月到而家<br />\n政府可以做嘅除咗靠黑警亂咁拉人打人<br />\n更重要嘅就係輿論戰<br />\n希望我哋內部出現分化<br />\n其實佢哋嘅做法就係將兩個和理同勇武兩類嘅抗爭者拉去兩個極端<br />\n<br />\n例子一：<br />\n剛剛開始有裝修行動嘅時候<br />\n五毛分咗兩類<br />\n一類想我哋無上限咁裝修<br />\n例如vans、所有藍店（小店，唔係優品中移動嗰啲）等等<br />\n另一類就不斷話裝修過咗火好暴力<br />\n再斷章取義邊個邊個外國議員或者報紙要同我哋割席<br />\n而根據人只會睇到自己相信嘅嘢呢個定律<br />\n好多人就會加入去譴責另一個極端嘅人太暴力或者太保守<br />\n而當時其實我哋早有有咗4色分類呢d原則<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係熱門佔嘅post主要都係風向、評論post為主<br />\n而唔係實際嘅行動、理念post</span><br />\n<br />\n我嘅結論係，我哋人數一定唔夠d五毛洗版咁勁，而且佢哋好識利用我哋嘅語言<br />\n而且寫過essay都知任何數據你都可以吹到符合你個point架啦<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋思考嘅時候就要諗到底一件事發生之後實際造成嘅影響係乜嘢</span>而唔係d五毛嘅煽情話語<br />\n<br />\n咁呢幾日嘅風向同實際影響又係咩呢？<br />\n咁就嚟到例子二：<br />\n五毛最新風向就係令鍾意開花嘅屌守大學嘅人<br />\n鍾意防守嘅覺得叫人撤守轉去開花係散水撚<br />\n常見論點有不斷吹話大學係大台，守大學係無意義、只會減少開花手足嘅數目<br />\n務求動搖同分化守喺大學嘅人，尤其是而家大學入面其實大部分都係外援<br />\n除咗斷章取義呢招，佢哋仲有一招就係將d好細微嘅嘢誇大<br />\n除咗五毛推post，我諗唔到點解只係一個冇禮貌嘅人守中大其中一個入口<br />\n呢d咁無聊嘅嘢都要喺熱門討論成日？<br />\n<br />\n咁講到尾，守大學嘅意義係咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n一、佔據交通要道<br />\ncu控制咗成個大埔九龍嘅出入，poly控制咗紅隧，city bu隔離係獅子山隧道，咁樣對於呢幾日黎明行動未打已經贏咗一半<br />\n而且中大開一條行車線呢步棋其實好完美咁show到而家個主導權就係喺抗爭者手上（除咗個開價係區選真係太on9之外）<br />\n由以前我哋等黑警主動清場，而家我哋可以轉守為攻<br />\n<br />\n二、抗爭由以前個個星期六日part time抗爭，變成24/7不分晝夜<br />\n呢個已經係一個好大嘅突破<br />\n點解呢幾日d狗唔出嚟？如果佢哋有能力令我哋停，我哋都唔會打咗到而家就快半年啦！<br />\n由班狗近日要去到要懲教做外援可以睇到，佢哋根本冇人手同時處理咁多間大學封路同埋各區同時開花<br />\n<br />\n三、群情洶湧，行動升級<br />\n如果當日冇中大守衛戰，點會有人去到燒天水圍警署，旺角開足一日一夜，黨鐵紅毛泥封西同拆路軌？<br />\n仲有今日有人可以日光日白掟燃燒彈令成條東鐵收皮<br />\n可以反映到兩樣野<br />\n一、就算好多手足去咗中大，依然可以多區有效開花<br />\n我哋嘅人數其實係因應民情而決定，開花唔夠人唔一定係因為大學分薄咗人手（事實上大學入面長期都唔夠人）<br />\n二、更加多人放下抗爭底線，成為魔法師<br />\n<br />\n四、行動升級，仲要轉守為攻<br />\n有去現場就知守大學嘅手足唔係無所事事<br />\n佢哋不斷咁研究同製造新法術<br />\n有咗呢d backup，我哋可以利用大學易守難攻嘅優勢，以大學為中心去附近開花<br />\n一來有足夠武器，二來可以有安全嘅撤退路線<br />\n喺度我建議各大學生會或者指揮部可以盡快成立游擊隊，夜晚聚夠人就可以晚晚開花<br />\n而我哋下一步要做嘅嘢就係搵下一個進攻嘅目標<br />\n以小弟愚見<br />\n首先黑警當然係要懲罰要清算<br />\n但係就算有黑警死咗，港共根本唔會在乎<br />\n經濟上都要繼續揸住港共同共產黨春袋<br />\n但係有工會嘅真罷工暫時都係未有機會發生<br />\n我認為佢哋最重要嘅都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主權、主權、主權</span><br />\n所以下一個目標要對準政府建築物，令香港政府停擺，將我哋嘅治權攞返黎<br />\n<br />\n小弟呢幾日都喺開花同各大院校中間徘徊<br />\n其實大家真係好有心，我亦都唔覺得有嘉年華氣氛<br />\n但係咁多年輕人其實佢哋真係好需要人帶領<br />\n佢哋有d人可能撳緊手機，吹水，有d可能真係要休息<br />\n但係當你叫佢哋幫忙<br />\n佢哋有嘅係無限嘅行動力，佢哋真係會好樂意<br />\n後生嘅你叫佢哋組織或者談判可能真係未夠成熟<br />\n但係邊個柒咗都好，大家同路人，係咪下下都要大大力屌呢？<br />\n之前睇過一篇前線訪問<br />\n點解前線個個都後生？係因為前線冇大人！<br />\n點解佢哋會做錯？因為我哋d大人唔夠人一齊幫佢哋<br />\n<br />\n唔經唔覺，我哋呢場革命已經打咗就快半年<br />\n我哋可以行到今時今日只因為一句說話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割席，不篤灰</span></span><br />\n香港人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命！</span>"},{"pid":"d047543676f718b017f0e4caba565383c029d3df","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"sorry我侮辱咗狗，佢哋係曱甴"},{"pid":"ad3d80c4298ff32233b93fb6ec1b7183c24bcf3f","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"求大家幫手推，唔好比五毛帶風向"},{"pid":"03f43ebcca8d8dc05cf8d878300fdd347963479a","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"習曱甴<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"b52ab3dfe28e588c18b0695ad9fcd7a7bfb35542","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"習曱甴<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"a4ed94218cdc2d4fa195e23e4f0e9789c3420b09","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:42:20.000Z","msg":"習曱甴<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"a5cb895257c9d9d5bf96e982ad83708f4e20f892","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"習曱甴<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"ad9b57a66732468bd72ef965c9918b44d2df53fb","tid":1723240,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700ac34c11ea10127490653385dc82a3dc066bcc","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:44:20.000Z","msg":"曹操話你知點解唔好捉鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1723153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1723153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n呢篇值得推"},{"pid":"97cbf6d47044b5562ad8d437991d1075e62bc79e","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad9b57a66732468bd72ef965c9918b44d2df53fb","tid":1723240,"uid":158546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"多謝手足幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2ad73c14e6f52b4da7b48b4cf6020c9b12391d","tid":1723240,"uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"五毛網上扮偏激既留言你阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越留多幾個<br />\n黑警現實混入扮示威者嫁禍比你，你又阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越做多幾單<br />\n<br />\n事實係你越比反應，越加把口去爭論<br />\n就越中分化計<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有你繼續做你認為啱既行動<br />\n講你認為有建設性既野<br />\n去洗走唔真實既行為同言論<br />\n令合理既行為同言論繼續佔有主流絕對比例<br />\n咁先有意思</span><br />\n<br />\n做好自己本份<br />\n你控制範圍內做到個part就做到最好<br />\n唔好比你控制唔到既野，動搖到你本身應該做既野<br />\n如果你停左唔再做，佢就真係成功阻止你<br />\n<br />\n香港人醒目少少，再輸分化就無下次機會<br />\n其他有咩唔認同既事，等贏左先再計"},{"pid":"3415faba31e391b30e9877b5ecc573b0df79b845","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b2ad73c14e6f52b4da7b48b4cf6020c9b12391d","tid":1723240,"uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"五毛網上扮偏激既留言你阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越留多幾個<br />\n黑警現實混入扮示威者嫁禍比你，你又阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越做多幾單<br />\n<br />\n事實係你越比反應，越加把口去爭論<br />\n就越中分化計<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有你繼續做你認為啱既行動<br />\n講你認為有建設性既野<br />\n去洗走唔真實既行為同言論<br />\n令合理既行為同言論繼續佔有主流絕對比例<br />\n咁先有意思</span><br />\n<br />\n做好自己本份<br />\n你控制範圍內做到個part就做到最好<br />\n唔好比你控制唔到既野，動搖到你本身應該做既野<br />\n如果你停左唔再做，佢就真係成功阻止你<br />\n<br />\n香港人醒目少少，再輸分化就無下次機會<br />\n其他有咩唔認同既事，等贏左先再計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"但係真係好多人會盲中中信咗五毛。。。"},{"pid":"d08fa413f1cd36b1eeef434bf557db7ff207ab99","tid":1723240,"uid":118082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c9bb0f6c28c03a06c2fa0a290842675dc52e562","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:40.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]邊撚個再話大學據點係鳩佔或者鼓吹棄守一律為風向分化撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722290</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n手足呢篇都分析得好好，有冇諗過我都係風向撚？"},{"pid":"59ee7087cc688887381b33aee8570be86778720d","tid":1723240,"uid":56633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2a931f256f543ac90119917af7fca2082e86cbd","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"幾時先推到上熱門？"},{"pid":"53b033181a448e6c131aa947e64a03691bac4599","tid":1723240,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3415faba31e391b30e9877b5ecc573b0df79b845","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b2ad73c14e6f52b4da7b48b4cf6020c9b12391d","tid":1723240,"uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"五毛網上扮偏激既留言你阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越留多幾個<br />\n黑警現實混入扮示威者嫁禍比你，你又阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越做多幾單<br />\n<br />\n事實係你越比反應，越加把口去爭論<br />\n就越中分化計<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有你繼續做你認為啱既行動<br />\n講你認為有建設性既野<br />\n去洗走唔真實既行為同言論<br />\n令合理既行為同言論繼續佔有主流絕對比例<br />\n咁先有意思</span><br />\n<br />\n做好自己本份<br />\n你控制範圍內做到個part就做到最好<br />\n唔好比你控制唔到既野，動搖到你本身應該做既野<br />\n如果你停左唔再做，佢就真係成功阻止你<br />\n<br />\n香港人醒目少少，再輸分化就無下次機會<br />\n其他有咩唔認同既事，等贏左先再計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"但係真係好多人會盲中中信咗五毛。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n永遠你有妙計時，人地都會有妙計<br />\n你有有效攻擊，一定一樣有有效攻擊<br />\n你打幾大力都無用，堅持唔倒下嗰個先係贏家"},{"pid":"37f90992e199410a81384c9fc1eba5686dc051a4","tid":1723240,"uid":129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40b5a1902ea2528b01f7eb540a4135e76ff049d5","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以睇穿五毛呢個［各走極端法］"},{"pid":"25cefc4b4929e7475e093d11e117fa62964d7cc9","tid":1723240,"uid":289557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"緊要<br />\n空氣推"},{"pid":"428bf543d6b9487bd0e70394e301fd5c369479af","tid":1723240,"uid":72442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4a4a435d44a6e692b4b2b4468fcd3d7b95b4f74","tid":1723240,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"aa78d7154ef11961c2c75b0464d9e6f54dfdf51b","tid":1723240,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ab28c184ae7eb3bac1975b65e5dfbaa0d8c595","tid":1723240,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"其實由我地守到中大開始<br />\n就已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n中大已經係一定要守嘅地方<br />\n面對抗爭逼住去第個階段吧啦<br />\n有好多戰況我地都未面對過<br />\n唔好再用以前啲佔金鐘「經驗」就覺得「有大台」「死守」一定死，因為今次個情況已經好唔同，成長啦，有好多新戰略我地都未見過<br />\n今次中大係一定要守！"},{"pid":"686de0ed8fd38ec8c1c655acc2349ff032ec57ae","tid":1723240,"uid":45925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c62790e546903e4ab02c8f3e270e1cf14d7133d","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"由6月到而家<br />\n政府可以做嘅除咗靠黑警亂咁拉人打人<br />\n更重要嘅就係輿論戰<br />\n希望我哋內部出現分化<br />\n其實佢哋嘅做法就係將兩個和理同勇武兩類嘅抗爭者拉去兩個極端<br />\n<br />\n例子一：<br />\n剛剛開始有裝修行動嘅時候<br />\n五毛分咗兩類<br />\n一類想我哋無上限咁裝修<br />\n例如vans、所有藍店（小店，唔係優品中移動嗰啲）等等<br />\n另一類就不斷話裝修過咗火好暴力<br />\n再斷章取義邊個邊個外國議員或者報紙要同我哋割席<br />\n而根據人只會睇到自己相信嘅嘢呢個定律<br />\n好多人就會加入去譴責另一個極端嘅人太暴力或者太保守<br />\n而當時其實我哋早有有咗4色分類呢d原則<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係熱門佔嘅post主要都係風向、評論post為主<br />\n而唔係實際嘅行動、理念post</span><br />\n<br />\n我嘅結論係，我哋人數一定唔夠d五毛洗版咁勁，而且佢哋好識利用我哋嘅語言<br />\n而且寫過essay都知任何數據你都可以吹到符合你個point架啦<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋思考嘅時候就要諗到底一件事發生之後實際造成嘅影響係乜嘢</span>而唔係d五毛嘅煽情話語<br />\n<br />\n咁呢幾日嘅風向同實際影響又係咩呢？<br />\n咁就嚟到例子二：<br />\n五毛最新風向就係令鍾意開花嘅屌守大學嘅人<br />\n鍾意防守嘅覺得叫人撤守轉去開花係散水撚<br />\n常見論點有不斷吹話大學係大台，守大學係無意義、只會減少開花手足嘅數目<br />\n務求動搖同分化守喺大學嘅人，尤其是而家大學入面其實大部分都係外援<br />\n除咗斷章取義呢招，佢哋仲有一招就係將d好細微嘅嘢誇大<br />\n除咗五毛推post，我諗唔到點解只係一個冇禮貌嘅人守中大其中一個入口<br />\n呢d咁無聊嘅嘢都要喺熱門討論成日？<br />\n<br />\n咁講到尾，守大學嘅意義係咩呢？<br />\n<br />\n一、佔據交通要道<br />\ncu控制咗成個大埔九龍嘅出入，poly控制咗紅隧，city bu隔離係獅子山隧道，咁樣對於呢幾日黎明行動未打已經贏咗一半<br />\n而且中大開一條行車線呢步棋其實好完美咁show到而家個主導權就係喺抗爭者手上（除咗個開價係區選真係太on9之外）<br />\n由以前我哋等黑警主動清場，而家我哋可以轉守為攻<br />\n<br />\n二、抗爭由以前個個星期六日part time抗爭，變成24/7不分晝夜<br />\n呢個已經係一個好大嘅突破<br />\n點解呢幾日d狗唔出嚟？如果佢哋有能力令我哋停，我哋都唔會打咗到而家就快半年啦！<br />\n由班狗近日要去到要懲教做外援可以睇到，佢哋根本冇人手同時處理咁多間大學封路同埋各區同時開花<br />\n<br />\n三、群情洶湧，行動升級<br />\n如果當日冇中大守衛戰，點會有人去到燒天水圍警署，旺角開足一日一夜，黨鐵紅毛泥封西同拆路軌？<br />\n仲有今日有人可以日光日白掟燃燒彈令成條東鐵收皮<br />\n可以反映到兩樣野<br />\n一、就算好多手足去咗中大，依然可以多區有效開花<br />\n我哋嘅人數其實係因應民情而決定，開花唔夠人唔一定係因為大學分薄咗人手（事實上大學入面長期都唔夠人）<br />\n二、更加多人放下抗爭底線，成為魔法師<br />\n<br />\n四、行動升級，仲要轉守為攻<br />\n有去現場就知守大學嘅手足唔係無所事事<br />\n佢哋不斷咁研究同製造新法術<br />\n有咗呢d backup，我哋可以利用大學易守難攻嘅優勢，以大學為中心去附近開花<br />\n一來有足夠武器，二來可以有安全嘅撤退路線<br />\n喺度我建議各大學生會或者指揮部可以盡快成立游擊隊，夜晚聚夠人就可以晚晚開花<br />\n而我哋下一步要做嘅嘢就係搵下一個進攻嘅目標<br />\n以小弟愚見<br />\n首先黑警當然係要懲罰要清算<br />\n但係就算有黑警死咗，港共根本唔會在乎<br />\n經濟上都要繼續揸住港共同共產黨春袋<br />\n但係有工會嘅真罷工暫時都係未有機會發生<br />\n我認為佢哋最重要嘅都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主權、主權、主權</span><br />\n所以下一個目標要對準政府建築物，令香港政府停擺，將我哋嘅治權攞返黎<br />\n<br />\n小弟呢幾日都喺開花同各大院校中間徘徊<br />\n其實大家真係好有心，我亦都唔覺得有嘉年華氣氛<br />\n但係咁多年輕人其實佢哋真係好需要人帶領<br />\n佢哋有d人可能撳緊手機，吹水，有d可能真係要休息<br />\n但係當你叫佢哋幫忙<br />\n佢哋有嘅係無限嘅行動力，佢哋真係會好樂意<br />\n後生嘅你叫佢哋組織或者談判可能真係未夠成熟<br />\n但係邊個柒咗都好，大家同路人，係咪下下都要大大力屌呢？<br />\n之前睇過一篇前線訪問<br />\n點解前線個個都後生？係因為前線冇大人！<br />\n點解佢哋會做錯？因為我哋d大人唔夠人一齊幫佢哋<br />\n<br />\n唔經唔覺，我哋呢場革命已經打咗就快半年<br />\n我哋可以行到今時今日只因為一句說話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割席，不篤灰</span></span><br />\n香港人，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命！</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c189036b09c81d7c10ebcad4c61afb9a4cffe7dc","tid":1723240,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a78c4bcc4ac56bddff66329373870a3a833f08b","tid":1723240,"uid":45925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b033181a448e6c131aa947e64a03691bac4599","tid":1723240,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3415faba31e391b30e9877b5ecc573b0df79b845","tid":1723240,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b2ad73c14e6f52b4da7b48b4cf6020c9b12391d","tid":1723240,"uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"五毛網上扮偏激既留言你阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越留多幾個<br />\n黑警現實混入扮示威者嫁禍比你，你又阻唔到<br />\n你越反感佢越做多幾單<br />\n<br />\n事實係你越比反應，越加把口去爭論<br />\n就越中分化計<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有你繼續做你認為啱既行動<br />\n講你認為有建設性既野<br />\n去洗走唔真實既行為同言論<br />\n令合理既行為同言論繼續佔有主流絕對比例<br />\n咁先有意思</span><br />\n<br />\n做好自己本份<br />\n你控制範圍內做到個part就做到最好<br />\n唔好比你控制唔到既野，動搖到你本身應該做既野<br />\n如果你停左唔再做，佢就真係成功阻止你<br />\n<br />\n香港人醒目少少，再輸分化就無下次機會<br />\n其他有咩唔認同既事，等贏左先再計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"但係真係好多人會盲中中信咗五毛。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n永遠你有妙計時，人地都會有妙計<br />\n你有有效攻擊，一定一樣有有效攻擊<br />\n你打幾大力都無用，堅持唔倒下嗰個先係贏家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"所以不分化不割席先贏到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c69c6cb335b8d7237af6640c30072eabf66c0fe","tid":1723240,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:14:49.000Z","msg":"推樓主"},{"pid":"064b28edbe54ff6974dd04596326d1502fb7f490","tid":1723240,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:15:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a304e0f3d337912f664b327ce98c2c2bf0cf2c7a","tid":1723240,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"三毛死全家"},{"pid":"33ec6730bc27552a223b15d8f0c81277ec0fabe9","tid":1723240,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3a268224902cd5dd1abbd30bf3188be23c6258","tid":1723240,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"總之結果就係想分化，引我地內鬥<br />\n知道d言論係帶咩風向就醒水"},{"pid":"4b6598e58a099c0f4ed05296e8ae2fd70bb71f78","tid":1723240,"uid":327031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"習曱甴<br />\n甴近平"},{"pid":"fe46522050fca1872f7343f54bfb3824886f6a11","tid":1723240,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas