g":"推你個post, 仲有唔好再叫錯啦.<br />\n<br />\n班藍絲咁中意侮辱人係曱甴, 我地就要以其之道還治其身,<br />\n黑警 = 曱甴, <br />\n習近平 = 甴近平 = 曱甴王<br />\n<br />\n樓主唔好再叫錯啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca01e228652fe1fbf158385de7a7297207394a64","tid":1723240,"uid":192540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"推 正視聽"},{"pid":"0573de71ce2e8d7a7ec8473a159d01eb6de8b021","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c2f5e7959f920300a96bdc031f1a8609ba48f7","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d32eceabf8fa94f4e1ad405001d4e1f66639a1","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc1b9ff09d6d64d9818df903b4e4d84df794ac5","tid":1723240,"uid":215501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:47:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"901f0547db8862e46993dae588f2fd3018777344","tid":1723240,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">澄明思諸，勿陷分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n捉鬼係永遠捉唔完，中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面<br />\n<br />\n平心而論，對家要收風根本唔會帶住支槍，帶得支槍入去理大就擺明預咗比你捉，達成佢地分化你地嘅政治目的，既然有鬼會帶住支槍，冇槍嘅鬼都肯定會有，黑臉白臉嘅鬼自然都會有齊曬，正如連登夠有五毛、TG各公海都一定會有對家臥底，呢個係common sense，所以我再重覆一次，<span style=\"color: red;\">中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面</span>"},{"pid":"9f10e943716f6898c707b487a8b6146eb0bddb9f","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0205224f6859d2be0f26e65455a56250c7fdfe24","tid":1723240,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"64cbbc27f43303cf1c60374a055af3962886ef7c","tid":1723240,"uid":104816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:53:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b274b53a352c568389ffc4feeca889cf31bfe403","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f84bf2728d1b5129be8fa0a1acc4b207dc726e","tid":1723240,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"正經post推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f88877f0638d94876b8c3204ce43e6a9b46d7e","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:01:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c549aa6fa2b8b7a9ceeaaba2ea3b5b4655754c","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ba762f499616c7ee0d49a54cc597e026c5edaf","tid":1723240,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T10:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}